{
  "stem": "1292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the spirit was such that we did keep up the spirit by talking-- saying-- telling jokes through the night, the young people and having-- we cried at the best time for ourself we could, right?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would socialize with the people mainly because it was-- as I remember, you couldn't go out after dark and things like this, so mostly it was the people that was neighboring or living with us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did try to do the best for ourselves--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, you mean for amusement?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we was often cooking together or we was singing together or we was trying to make the most out of a very bad time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was a time of fear for the future.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a time to be very uncertain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I married in August, as I said, 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very young and the tendency there to marry-- a lot of young girls did marry because, silly as it sounds today, it was such attitude we didn't want to die as virgin.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today that is very stupid, but that was the morality then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a girl who wasn't virgin when she married was did have the idea that her husband would not respect her, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so really this way I think that most girls was very moral.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I married two-- there was two weddings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have some very unhappy memories on the day of my wedding because I went to a hairdresser, and I did try to look good for the wedding.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was called to work to mend the socks on my way home by a German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was absolutely frantic because I said, you know, people-- I'm going to my wedding.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
